text:
Yo POOTA
You've always been the responsible one in our group. So many fond memories with you man. Photography trips se lekr Galaxy jeetna to Z Square ghoomna. Nainital, Roorkee, Banaras, Lucknow, Manali. You've been a constant. Bus me bhaang pe high in Banaras, that story in Ramaiyya at 3am, tereko matress ke saath room se nikalna. Kuch bhi ho, barging into your room to talk to you and Vaibhav was always my first option. Bhai padhai Antaragni bakchodi sab manage kiya tune..Kaafi chaapu ho be tum. Yaar kya likhu mai ab. Hoping to have numerous great trips with you in future. GOA baaki hai abhi to:-P.

text:
PRATI PRATI PRATI
So much to say but in a lack of words. You know I love you man!
You've been an amazing friend Vaibhav. Almost saare college memories saath me hi hai tere. First year me raat ko campus ghoomna, chicken order krna, mere liye model banna:-P. Bhai club me bhi ek saath rahe apan. Nainital, Roorkee, Lucknow, Banaras and finally Manali, kaafi maza kiya be saath me. Thanks for selecting what photo I should post on instagram, kaunsa edit accha hai. Bc puri insta feed tere se puchke daali hai maine. Respect man! Design me tereko itni mehnat krte huye dekha hai. You disappoint none, apna kaam chorke doosro ki help krta hai. Be this innocent. Mehnat krte raho. I wish we stay friends like this forever. Agli trip GOA krte hai. Hawas bachake rakho:-P
author: Utkarsh  Maken
